YBIKE Pewi
Pewi is an innovative foot to floor ride-on for children. Pewi is the coolest, sleekest walker around. Unlike traditional walkers, the Pewi actually enhances body and space awareness. With the Pewi the child stands freely in front of the walker as an aid.

**Features**
* Multi direction caster wheels allow a child to ride and easily control the Pewi in any direction
* Ideal use for indoor and outdoor play on smooth surfaces
* Non marking rubber wheels that will not damage or mark floors
* Ideal for early stage balance and motor skill development
* Recommended ages: 12 - 36 months
* Max weight: 44 lbs

